cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with person re-identification using visible-infrared images. The paper also involves deep learning techniques, which makes it relevant to the machine learning (cs.MM) and machine learning sub-categories (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper proposes a novel method for disentangling ID-discriminative factors and ID-excluded factors, which is related to the field of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper involves the use of infrared images, which is related to the sub-category of information retrieval (cs.IR).
